content:
Manage Permission Sets Efficiently

Assign the new permission sets, such as TPM Funds Calculation Worker and CGCloud Retail Supervisor User, to users. The new permission sets are now shipped with the managed package and are automatically updated whenever the managed package is upgraded.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Consumer Goods Cloud is enabled.

How: If you're using Retail Execution or Trade Promotion Management, use new profiles and assign the new permission sets based on user roles.
title: Managing Permission Sets in Salesforce
